# OrangeHRM Automation Framework (Selenium + Java + TestNG)

## Project Description
This project is a Selenium Automation Framework built using Java, TestNG, and Maven.
It automates the login functionality of the OrangeHRM demo application.

 Application Under Test:
https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/

---

## Tech Stack
- Java 17
- Selenium WebDriver 4
- TestNG
- Maven
- WebDriverManager
- Page Object Model (POM)

---

## Features Automated
- Valid Login Test
- Invalid Login Test
- Explicit Wait Handling
- Screenshot Capture on Failure
- TestNG Assertions
- Page Object Model implementation

---

## Framework Structure
- Base Layer (Browser setup & teardown)
- Page Layer (Login Page)
- Test Layer (TestNG Test Classes)
- Utility Layer (Screenshot Utility)

---

## How to Run
1. Clone the repository
2. Import as Maven project
3. Run using testng.xml
